159
00:09:51,962 --> 00:09:53,262
Okay.

160
00:09:54,462 --> 00:09:57,362
Okay, I'll go check the roof, then.

161
00:09:57,362 --> 00:09:58,562
Okay.

162
00:10:03,862 --> 00:10:05,762
