170
00:10:20,962 --> 00:10:22,462
Mitsuhiko.

171
00:10:22,462 --> 00:10:23,762
Okay.

172
00:10:23,762 --> 00:10:25,862
I'll go search upstairs.

173
00:10:25,862 --> 00:10:28,062
